a great sign of respect.

265
00:16:10,804 --> 00:16:12,764
Respect?

266
00:16:12,764 --> 00:16:14,682
Okay, okay.

267
00:16:14,682 --> 00:16:16,016
I can do that.

268
00:16:16,016 --> 00:16:17,685
