is to share your company

278
00:16:41,542 --> 00:16:43,503
and do honor to your name."

279
00:16:43,503 --> 00:16:45,421
Then what?

280
00:16:46,965 --> 00:16:49,676
Well, either she accepts
your offer...

281
00:16:51,594 --> 00:16:53,471
