my uniforms?

297
00:17:40,935 --> 00:17:43,437
Garak finished the alterations
and...

298
00:17:43,437 --> 00:17:45,189
he sent these along.

299
00:17:45,189 --> 00:17:47,567
He guarantees
the insoles will help your feet.

300
00:17:47,567 --> 00:17:49,109
Ow, ow...
<i>ow!</i>

301
00:17:49,109 --> 00:17:50,987
That wasn't
very convincing.

302
00:17:50,987 --> 00:17:52,989
I think she's actually
enjoying it, Miles.

303
00:17:52,989 --> 00:17:55,867
You better press harder
if you want her to suffer.

304
00:17:55,867 --> 00:17:58,578
Harder, it is.

305
00:17:58,578 --> 00:18:00,580
Ow, ooh!

306
00:18:00,580 --> 00:18:04,124
