342
00:20:05,913 --> 00:20:08,916
Grilka loved it--
all of it--
everything I did.

343
00:20:08,916 --> 00:20:12,753
Everything I said
was perfect.

344
00:20:12,753 --> 00:20:16,298
So, I know nothing
about Klingon women.

345
00:20:16,298 --> 00:20:18,759
She said I had the heart
of a<i> Basai</i> Master--

346
00:20:18,759 --> 00:20:20,887
