It is a poet.

347
00:20:20,887 --> 00:20:24,765
A poet? I guess
I can live with that.

348
00:20:27,518 --> 00:20:29,062
What else happened?

349
00:20:29,062 --> 00:20:30,646
She spent
about an hour

350
00:20:30,646 --> 00:20:32,690
