00:20:57,256 --> 00:20:59,800
Her bodyguard was giving me
threatening looks all night.

361
00:20:59,800 --> 00:21:02,970
That is to be expected.
The idea of a Ferengi

362
00:21:02,970 --> 00:21:06,432
