in this time--

399
00:23:18,231 --> 00:23:23,485
a thousand years ago,
the dawn of the Empire.

400
00:23:23,485 --> 00:23:27,240
500 warriors stormed the
Great Hall at Qam-Chee.

401
00:23:27,240 --> 00:23:30,117
The city garrison
fled before them.

402
00:23:30,117 --> 00:23:33,411
Only the Emperor Kahless
and the Lady Lukara

403
00:23:33,411 --> 00:23:35,206
stood their ground.

404
00:23:35,206 --> 00:23:37,415
It was here that they began

405
00:23:37,415 --> 00:23:39,585
the greatest romance
in Klingon history.

406
00:23:39,585 --> 00:23:43,297
This is ridiculous.
Ah!

407
00:23:43,297 --> 00:23:46,092
I'm surrounded by corpses.

408
00:23:46,092 --> 00:23:48,219
My shoes are dripping in blood,

409
00:23:48,219 --> 00:23:50,888
and you want me
to feel romantic?

410
00:23:52,472 --> 00:23:54,934
Why am I putting myself
through this?

411
00:23:54,934 --> 00:23:58,354
Because later that night,
Kahless and Lukara

412
00:23:58,354 --> 00:24:02,149
