is outrageous!

454
00:26:04,855 --> 00:26:06,648
You forget yourself,
Thopok.

455
00:26:06,648 --> 00:26:08,692
You are the Commander
of the Lady's Guard,

456
00:26:08,692 --> 00:26:10,236
nothing more.

457
00:26:10,236 --> 00:26:12,946
Do not presume
to judge her.

458
00:26:12,946 --> 00:26:15,366
(<i> Quark and Grilka laughing</i> )

459
00:26:18,702 --> 00:26:20,371
(<i> shrieks</i> )

460
00:26:20,371 --> 00:26:23,790
Tumek, Maporian
ale for two.

461
00:26:23,790 --> 00:26:25,167
Mistress.

462
00:26:25,167 --> 00:26:28,504
You are an interesting man.

463
00:26:28,504 --> 00:26:29,880
I always thought so.

464
00:26:29,880 --> 00:26:31,673
Not much of a
fighter, of course.

465
00:26:31,673 --> 00:26:33,133
Fortunately for you,

466
00:26:33,133 --> 00:26:35,094
