holo-warriors.

467
00:26:35,094 --> 00:26:37,096
Well, it's the thought
that counts.

468
00:26:37,096 --> 00:26:39,390
Yes, it is.

469
00:26:39,390 --> 00:26:41,975
And what are your
thoughts, Quark?

470
00:26:41,975 --> 00:26:45,145
Why play out one of
the most romantic scenes

471
00:26:45,145 --> 00:26:47,314
in Klingon literature for me?

472
00:26:47,314 --> 00:26:50,359
Why learn to
speak Klingon

473
00:26:50,359 --> 00:26:52,194
and observe our customs?

474
00:26:55,030 --> 00:26:57,575
Why do you pursue me?

475
00:26:57,575 --> 00:27:01,078
I only pursue those things
I wish to acquire.

476
00:27:01,078 --> 00:27:04,039
"Acquire"?

477
00:27:04,039 --> 00:27:07,460
Now you sound like
a Ferengi again.

478
00:27:07,460 --> 00:27:10,421
I<i> am</i>  a Ferengi.
That means I have a talent

479
00:27:10,421 --> 00:27:12,714
for appreciating objects
of great value.

480
00:27:12,714 --> 00:27:16,343
And I believe
you may be worth

481
00:27:16,343 --> 00:27:19,054
more than all the latinum
in the Quadrant.

482
00:27:26,728 --> 00:27:28,730
My Kahless.

483
00:27:31,150 --> 00:27:32,692
My Lukara.

484
00:27:32,692 --> 00:27:34,945
(<i> yelling in rage</i> )

485
00:27:36,280 --> 00:27:38,031
