486
00:27:38,031 --> 00:27:39,450
Forgive me, Mistress,

487
00:27:39,450 --> 00:27:41,327
but I cannot watch
this any longer.

488
00:27:41,327 --> 00:27:42,995
I will not protect a House

489
00:27:42,995 --> 00:27:44,746
