Ferengi.

490
00:27:44,746 --> 00:27:48,167
You are a coward
and a liar,

491
00:27:48,167 --> 00:27:50,336
and you have no honor.

492
00:27:50,336 --> 00:27:56,216
So tomorrow, you will kill me,
or I<i> will</i> kill you.

493
00:28:11,064 --> 00:28:13,484
Home two hours early?

494
