00:28:25,787 --> 00:28:27,623
(<i> door opens</i> )

499
00:28:27,623 --> 00:28:29,041
Hi!

500
00:28:29,041 --> 00:28:30,917
Hi.

501
00:28:30,917 --> 00:28:33,753
KEIKO:
Sit down. You
